       <div class="modulecc"> 
        <div class="modulecnt"> 
         <div class="log1">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/92906.htm" target="_blank">2012年05月07日&nbsp;&nbsp;初 夏</a>
         </div> 
         <div class="log2">
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 40pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">夏天，让人想到的是热，但初夏的天气却是宜人的，正如宋朝诗人陆游说得：“纷纷红紫已成尘，布谷声中夏令新。”春天那些万紫千红的花朵已经凋零，我们在布谷鸟的歌唱中迎来了初夏。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt">
             <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /-->
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 40pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">立夏，在嘉善有个习俗，那就是吃咸蛋、白煮肉、塌饼</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">……..</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">小时候一直盼望着到立夏，不但可以吃到自家做的点心，还能在大人做塌饼时候，乘机也在旁边做几个玩玩，卡看自己的手艺如何。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 40pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">塌饼的做法可是大有讲究。淘糯米、碾成粉、用水和、加豆沙、做成团</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">……</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">这些步骤一个都不能少。这些看似简单的程序，里边却有深深的奥妙，如核桃先在微波炉内加热变熟，在和粉的时候</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">加入民间田埂边上的“草头”，那是一种有助于消化的草药。锅内烧煮后连水一起和糯米粉和在一起，反复的糅合，使面粉变得更加的有筋道。最后加入在锅里闷煮过滤的精心用糖熬之的赤豆沙。奶奶总是把豆沙放的满满的，仿佛要将塌饼撑破似的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">杨万里写道“小荷才露尖尖角，早有蜻蜓立上头。”给了人们无限的遐想，看着荷叶和蝌蚪，仿佛看见了“接天连叶无穷碧，映月荷花别样红。”听见了蛙声阵阵。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 初夏在藕断丝连的塌饼和一角小小的荷叶中过去，留给人们对它的无限留恋和遐想。</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         </div> 
         <div class="log3">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/92906.htm" target="_blank">查看原文</a>┆评论(1)┆类别(
