         </div> 
         <div class="log1">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/83544.htm" target="_blank">2010年09月16日&nbsp;&nbsp;春 满 嘉 善</a>
         </div> 
         <div class="log2">
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">寒冷的冬天走了。到处是春姑娘的足迹：金黄的油菜花、火红的山茶花、雪白的玉兰花……春天溢满了嘉善！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
             <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /-->
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">你看，远远望去，一大片一大片的紫荆花整整齐齐地排在路两旁，就像是春姑娘的仪仗队，又好像是一条条紫色的绸带。近看，紫荆花爬满枝头，似乎要把天空占为已有。一簇堆在一簇上，多得不可计数，让人惊叹！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">晋阳路上的玉兰花也不甘示弱，一朵朵争奇斗艳，竞相开放。那玉兰花真白啊！好像是婴儿的小脸，那么纯洁；又好像银河中的点点繁星；那玉兰花真美啊！就像汉白玉做的杯子；那玉兰花真醒目啊！在午夜十二点的时候，闪闪发光，格外耀眼。啊，太美啦！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">不知不觉中，我漫步走到了市民广场。那儿的樱花可多了，长得遮天蔽日，一朵朵粉红色的小花布满天空，像天上的繁星，把天空染成了粉红色。风一吹，花瓣随风飘散，像一只只蝴蝶在翻飞，又像天女散花。粉红色的花瓣和青草相间在一起，像是给大地穿上了一件粉红色的大衣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">春姑娘还来到了我家里。外婆家门前的油菜花可高了，和我一般高。一眼望去，像是无边无际的金色海洋。君子兰也开了，高大的绿叶像侍卫一样，保护着娇嫩的花皇后。最令人兴奋地是，我家的仙人球开花了！一朵朵黄色的小花像一顶小帽子带在它的头上，感觉很别扭，又像一顶皇冠，扣在它头上，它又变成了威武的国王。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
             <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000">这真是春满嘉善，花满人间。嘉善拥有了春天，春天也拥有了嘉善！</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         </div> 
         <div class="log3">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/83544.htm" target="_blank">查看原文</a>┆评论(0)┆类别(
          <a href="logs.asp?cls=" target="_blank"></a>
          <a href="logs.asp?cls=0" target="_blank">默认类别</a>)┆发表于 2010/9/16 20:00:05
         </div> 
         <div class="log1">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/83546.htm" target="_blank">2010年09月16日&nbsp;&nbsp;人 类 的 罪 证</a>
         </div> 
         <div class="log2">
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><font size="5"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">知了知了</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">”,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">蝉先生热得直叫唤；“汪，汪”小狗吐着舌头</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">走来走去不知所措；“哧溜</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">哧溜”孩子们大口大口地吃着冷饮。今年夏天可真热啊！去年最高温度</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">39</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">℃</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">今年却突破</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">40</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">℃。今年的夏天为什么这么热呢？让我们来找找原因吧。</span></font></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><font size="5"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">原因一：废气排放。随着人们收入的增加</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">生活质量得到了很大的改善</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">以前出门靠两条腿</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">家里有辆自行车会引来无数羡慕的眼光</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">可是现在汽车越来越多的进入到家庭中</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">人们的腿再也迈不开大步</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">出门需要四个轮子代替</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">随之而来的便是越来越多的废气排出</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">导致气温上升</span></font></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><font size="5"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">原因二：温室效应。现在的家庭大部分都装上了空调</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">人们好像已经不习惯离开空调的日子了。阴凉的树荫下、晚饭过后的黄昏，已经很难觅到手摇蒲扇乘凉的人们。家家户户门窗紧闭</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">空调外机不时传来“嗡嗡”的噪杂声，同时也释放大量的热气，温室效应也导致天气越来越热。</span></font></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">原因三：光污染。现在的建筑大量使用玻璃，城市的繁华离不开大量的霓虹灯，由此引起光污染导致的气温升高。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><font size="5"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">另外由于人口的密集度越来越高</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">天气越来越热</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">导致恶性循环</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">,</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">于是气温一浪高过一浪。</span></font></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">今年炎热的气温造成了许多后果，让我们大家一起来看看。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">后果一：广西一养殖户的鸡棚里有成千只鸡死亡，原因是天气太热。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font color="#000000"><font size="5"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">后果二：台湾有</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">91</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">人因中暑而死亡。</span></font></font></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">后果三：南极上空的臭氧层空洞逐渐扩大。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">后果四：北极的冰山开始融化，许多北极熊无“家”可归。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">据科学家们的推测，再过几年，风景怡人的马尔代夫和一些美丽的海滨城市将会变成汪洋大海，不复存在。</font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><font color="#000000" size="5">看看这些可怕的后果，多么触目惊心啊！为了我们的地球、为了我们的家园、为了我们的子孙后代，请大家一定要保护环境。从我做起，从你做起，从身边的小事做起。少开汽车，多骑自行车，多步行，要知道每买一辆自行车就等于种一棵树；少用餐巾纸、一次性筷子、塑料袋，多用手帕、环保袋。让我们都来关爱自然，热爱地球吧！手挽手，肩并肩，心连心，节约资源，保护环境，捍卫地球，地球的明天一定会更加美好！</font></span></p>
         </div> 
         <div class="log3">
          <a href="http://blog.js0573.com/u/yeyc201/file/83546.htm" target="_blank">查看原文</a>┆评论(0)┆类别(
